            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h3>手机客户端</h3>
                <p><img class="qr-img" src="//n.sinaimg.cn/finance/niuyan2017/images/app_qr.png" alt="手机客户端"></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ft">Copyright &#169; 1996 - 2018 SINA Corporation, All Rights Reserved 新浪公司 <a target="_blank" href="http://www.sina.com.cn/intro/copyright.shtml">版权所有</a>
    </div>
</div>
